br />\nBetween,<br />\n<br />\n如果你電話上咗 WiFi，我估你部電話同部腦應該喺同一個 subnet，電話上唔到 webserver 應該唔關 port forwarding 事。<br />\nPort forwarding 應該係當你要用隻街外嘅 host (例如電話上流動網絡唔係上 WiFi 嗰陣) 上個 webserver 嗰陣先要搞的說。"},{"pid":"acaeeee4b37b6fe02016690b43f2f9077745949a","tid":598812,"uid":114766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5fcc88e97078c17da2d704c9a07bf3035a21be7","tid":598812,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T00:39:41.000Z","msg":"係咪喺 Windows 裝 xampp?<br />\n係嘅話有冇喺 Windows Firewall 開放返個 port 80 出嚟 ?<br />\n<br />\nBetween,<br />\n<br />\n如果你電話上咗 WiFi，我估你部電話同部腦應該喺同一個 subnet，電話上唔到 webserver 應該唔關 port forwarding 事。<br />\nPort forwarding 應該係當你要用隻街外嘅 host (例如電話上流動網絡唔係上 WiFi 嗰陣) 上個 webserver 嗰陣先要搞的說。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:24:59.000Z","msg":"Firewall 開放80係邊到整？<br />\n依家係電話用wifi入192.168.0.1/link and 用4g 入real ip/link 都404forbidden <br />\n但唔識睇error log"},{"pid":"1211debd66a86047338b56c3fc30435b32bf4e37","tid":598812,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:54:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wiki.mcneel.com/zoo/window7firewall\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.mcneel.com%2Fzoo%2Fwindow7firewall&d=C88rzUCsV2hIq0hYYhme%2FfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7c0fe019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.mcneel.com/zoo/window7firewall</a>"},{"pid":"5229e8b3697a4a573d327c0f591ea00e36933744","tid":598812,"uid":114766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1211debd66a86047338b56c3fc30435b32bf4e37","tid":598812,"uid":81021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T01:54:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://wiki.mcneel.com/zoo/window7firewall\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.mcneel.com%2Fzoo%2Fwindow7firewall&d=C88rzUCsV2hIq0hYYhme%2FfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7c0fe019\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://wiki.mcneel.com/zoo/window7firewall</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:46:54